    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the Double VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The factory suspension geometry remains precise, and the braking system provides firm, fade-free modulation. Finished in showroom-quality Carbon Black, the exterior exhibits exceptional paint depth with zero oxidation, while the Nappa leather interior shows no bolster wear. This is a collector-grade specimen with a fully documented service history and no deferred maintenance.",
